article.description: — Michael Forrest had 24 points as Florida Atlantic got past North Dakota 98-79 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Forrest scores 24 to lift FAU past North Dakota 98-79
article.linkText: Forrest scores 24 to lift FAU past North Dakota 98-79
article.story: BOCA RATON, Fla. -- — Michael Forrest had 24 points as Florida Atlantic got past North Dakota 98-79 on Saturday night. Bryan Greenlee had 14 points for Florida Atlantic (3-2). Giancarlo Rosado and Everett Winchester had 11 points. Caleb Nero scored 23 points for the Fighting Hawks (2-2). Matt Norman and Paul Bruns each had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
